title: Who is Nayeon of Twice dating in 2020? - Quora

response.answer_text: I'm sorry, I don't know. There are only rumours at the moment, nothing has been confirmed. There are also shippers but we all know how believable those are. She could be involved with someone, she could be casually dating or she could simply be happily single. It's not really any of our business but it's normal to be curious. Have a wonderful day, I hope someone makes you FEEL SPECIAL!

As of now, Nayeon hasn't been confirmed to have been dating anyone so far this year. As of now only Twice members Momo and Jihyo are in confirmed relationships with Heechul and Kang Daniel respectively.
